     Z S E R I O  C + +  R E F L E C T I O N


Build
=====

> mkdir build && cd build
> cmake -DZSERIO_RT_DIR=<path/to/zserio/compiler/extensions/cpp/runtime/src> ..
> cmake --build .

Test
====

> cd runtime && ctest --verbose
